+ *  INT_MESSAGE_RCV_DWNCL   (hypervisor message available)
+ *  INT_DEV_INTR_DWNCL      (device interrupt)
+ *  INT_DMATLB_MISS_DWNCL   (DMA TLB miss)
+ *  INT_SNITLB_MISS_DWNCL   (SNI TLB miss)
